366
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:04,210
Okay.

367
00:16:04,250 --> 00:16:05,920
I'll tell your dad the good news.

368
00:16:06,610 --> 00:16:08,280
Good boy.

369
00:16:08,970 --> 00:16:09,680
