385
00:16:57,680 --> 00:17:00,210
He's a very sweet man,

386
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:02,920
very attentive, has high empathy

387
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:04,850
and a good listener.

388
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,880
