534
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:20,930
as soon as he arrived.

535
00:22:21,410 --> 00:22:23,250
If the two of them really get together,

536
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:24,730
it will be

537
00:22:24,890 --> 00:22:26,760
