538
00:22:26,970 --> 00:22:27,600
Then

539
00:22:27,650 --> 00:22:29,490
Fang Lie will really have no hope.

540
00:22:30,650 --> 00:22:31,320
By the way,

541
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:33,930
