554
00:23:04,970 --> 00:23:05,650
Okay.

555
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:07,600
Mission accomplished. I'll be on my way.

556
00:23:07,650 --> 00:23:08,360
Bye.

557
00:23:08,360 --> 00:23:09,120
Xiaoqi.

558
00:23:10,570 --> 00:23:12,570
