769
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:31,730
Hello.

770
00:32:32,650 --> 00:32:34,040
I am the CEO of Future Group.

771
00:32:35,170 --> 00:32:36,010
My name is Fang Leng.

772
00:32:49,170 --> 00:32:50,210
